Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:04.22,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs64\pos(640,492)}某地          同人商店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:04.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,萌~萌~萌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,各位亲爱的宅男同胞们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失礼了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:23.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,现在这里由我们兽人新领域开拓联盟占领了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,现在店内被卷帘挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,无法直接确认里面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过根据逃出来的客人所说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,犯罪集团的成员是六名兽人族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:07.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,全员都拥有武装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:12.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,共有4名没来得及跑的店员跟客人  被当成人质关在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,犯人的要求是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:16.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:22.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们兽人新领域开拓联盟要求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:26.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,将工口漫画的主流改为「兽人x公主骑士」噗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,噗哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,身体还是很老实的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去了~要去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:40.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还要加入「兽人x精灵」「兽人x修女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,尽可能开拓新领域！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:48.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,总之就是  兽人x魔女娘  兽人x女教师  兽人xOL  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,它们要求开拓这些新领域本子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,虽然这要求很蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,署长  问题在于他们是他种族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,半兽人族及他种族的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:01.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是受到他种族间交流法保护的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们警察奈何不了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:07.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,连逮捕犯罪者都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,毕竟法案实行不久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还满是漏洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:14.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,别说得事不关己一样  外务省
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这种时候哪还能管那个法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你可以不遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但不止被解雇还会被逮捕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没人说要违抗法令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们就是为此而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个咖啡好难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是喝咖啡的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你们他种族间交流法保安局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,应该能解决这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你要交给她们来处理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要怎么接近犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:49.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,兽人族的鼻子都很灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:55.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大社团还没出名时出的稀有作品  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦  有女忍者在偷窥啊  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要这样说的话要说女忍  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,长相还算不错  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯  为什么会注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,气味  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:21.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们兽人族能嗅出一公里外女人的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以警察也无法持枪靠近我们  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,刚刚是不是有枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你这个气味控的变态猪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:32.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我对说话难听的女人没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂  是警察噗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,刚才处决了一名突入店内的女队员  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,当然是正当防卫  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.55,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为这个女人违反他种族间交流法袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.11,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我们就把她杀了噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我没下过突击命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,女队员是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是谁擅自行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,虽然十分不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但似乎必须要依靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们已经做好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还有个藏在角落的  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和魔女娘魔子妹妹长得一模一样！噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在这么小的店都没发现她  你们在干什么  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,给我好好确认  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谁来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不用这么害怕  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们都是绅士  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:52.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不会对女孩子做过分的事情  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,会遵守他种族间交流法  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,来交流下吧  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:07.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请各位警察看看我们他种族间的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只有队长享受太狡猾了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我我我  我们也想加入  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真没办法  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那就按顺序来  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,按照计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,把全员聚集到窗口了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,碍事的百叶窗也被扯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样就能看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,枪被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没闻到枪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:53.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,难道是在我们半径一公里的嗅觉范围外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,进行超长距离的精密狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到底是何方神圣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,待机时间太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大楼的风太大  眼睛都干涩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.62,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs44\pos(676,558)}单眼族  玛娜可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是有必要在两公里外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,难不成是惹人厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么办  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们没有备用的枪  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,冷静  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们还有人质
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:31.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么  这个巨汉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,各位人质们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快趁现在去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,缇奥是女孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:55.56,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,560)\fs44}鬼人族   缇奥尼西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:57.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人质都跑了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,冷…冷静点  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这里还有一个人质  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,用她做肉盾就行了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但…但是  枪被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那把我的枪借你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然装死装得那么逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是穿了防弹衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此就在我的拥抱下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,把你的里脊…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,把你的脊椎骨勒个粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的  又开了这么多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:47.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样下去我会被铅弹害到体重马赫数飙升的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为…为什么你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是世界第一精力充沛的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,奏比娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.25,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs44\pos(722,572)}活尸族    奏比娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还不快跪下  你们这些萌猪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只剩你一个了  黑猪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要接近我  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没看到这个人质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:11.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再靠近的话我就把她的细脖子给扭断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,兽人族真是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:24.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在这种同人商店怎么可能有女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,以为我是和魔女娘魔子妹妹长得一模一样的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,很遗憾  我是多佩尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:34.28,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs44\pos(698,564)}镜像人族   多佩尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,亏我那么相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,从两公里外跑来很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且这来福枪还很重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,玛娜辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过玛娜的那把来福真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:50.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,把枪身改短双持的话肯定很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,手臂会断的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你们这么轻松真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我可是被那头猪性骚扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你去把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:03.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,佩尔酱  吵架的话不行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在吃什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能以强制力处理的他种族引发的犯罪行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:14.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为了应对  由他种族所组成的特别部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H781777&\3c&HBEC3C4&}M  O  N！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster's  NewLaw
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快  老实点投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还是说你想变成煎猪排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:38.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我知道了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我投降  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啊  各位真强  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是我们的完败  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是但是但是…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,像这样投降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你们就不能对我使用暴力了  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,惩罚顶多就是强制遣返而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在干什么  噗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,虽说是橡皮弹不过你还真耐打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作为人类居然对他种族下手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这是违反他种族间交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么  墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,多佩尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,虽然同为他种族就没有法律规范了  不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,下手太重可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:34.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,给拿着低廉薪水的我增加多余工作的小猪们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看来需要些惩罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.96,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,有关今日的挟持事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.30,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,由于犯罪分子是他种族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.77,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,引起不小的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真不平静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不法分子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就没有身为种族代表的自觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.42,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs46\pos(734,466)}他种族引发挟持事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.42,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(428,444)}6人被逮捕  无人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请问专家丘矢田老师  您的看法是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦  墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:04.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎呀  果然Darling君泡的咖啡就是好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你用了混合的咖啡豆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是  是速溶的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:15.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对了对了！我今天有叫同事来  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:15.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,来白吃白喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你好  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}MON！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂  有听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:58.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不许动！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,住在这里的他种族给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你有违反交流法的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,乖乖束手就擒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我说比娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这里到处都是蜘蛛网好诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,缇奥  我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好像被什么绊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,幸好我是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要是活着早已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,比我这个没出场机会的人好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:42.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这是那个跑掉的魔物娘留下的纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,上面写着这里的住址
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:47.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大概是那个自称监督的人调查的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为她发了SOS求救所以我们去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,私自外出了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是逃走了才对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们也还没掌握情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:03.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个男人并没有登记为寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但为什么有他种族住在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去超市的晚间促销了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,差不多快回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你们从刚才开始一直在搬什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:20.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦  因为家门口掉了许多吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们就捡回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我应该是从超市回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抓到你的时候居然就昏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人类真是脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,令人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是拉克涅拉·阿拉克涅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是第一次见到阿剌克涅族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:00.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你好  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是啊！是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:12.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个  脑袋要充血了  可以放我下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你相当悠闲的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个硬汉游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:27.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要不要试试看你能玩到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真不像样  已经开始叫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:38.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不知是由于正义感还是什么而打破哈耳庇厄族的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,结果也和其他人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:46.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,本来还想说在抓之前先剥掉他伪善者的外皮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,期待落空了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有…有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有人报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蜘蛛网  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,听好了  不许发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果你出声求救的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂  有什么东西变硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被发现了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是  这是生理现象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好危险  好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真亏你能咬的住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真棒  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太…太诡异了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:57.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,听好了  现在支撑你的只有脚跟嘴上的丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,从这个高度掉下去  会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为你太调皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要惩罚一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么样  重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎啦哎啦  意外地能坚持呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拼命忍耐着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那这样还能忍住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,连这种地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然能咬断我的丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看来你不止那里硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,死  还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,各种意义上的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍微有点做过头了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个  拉克涅拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是和我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和寄宿家庭的人一起不是更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:12.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我和寄宿家庭的人合不来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:12.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:17.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他们大概以为会来个比较柔弱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:23.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那副像是吃了黄连一样的表情真是杰作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:29.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有个可疑大叔来求他们转让寄宿权
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛  他们想甩掉我这个麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太过分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我先说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我可不是希望你同情我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只是厌烦人类而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是对那些嘴上说着漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,却无法接受自己以外的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人类感到厌烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你也是那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:19:00.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你的下半身也是对我和人类一样的这部分起了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:05.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而这部分不过是让你充满生理厌恶感的肉块罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:14.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这些脚  怎么说呢…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,非常妖艳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.03,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs70\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(246,563)}足控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然对蜘蛛的脚发情  真是十足的变态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你就这么饥渴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,难不成你是处男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我我我…才不是处男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不知道什么时候叫了救援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,之前都是拖延时间的演技吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.48,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,完全被包围了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这里是他种族间交流…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,协调员  墨须
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对你警告！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你对自称电影监督的男性施加了暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这在法律上是决不被允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:05.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,现在立刻投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不然我们就将强制执行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谢谢你的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此我就把他当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:19.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,的确我昨天把他痛打了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是  那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:23.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,无论理由如何  暴力就是暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:31.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等等  听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她们说的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你不觉得是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:39.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:40.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我去自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拉克涅拉小姐  就快点逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:51.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,祝我好运？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:58.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:08.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我相当中意你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不仅选错了寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还疏忽了善后管理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:21.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不  没什么  我也不是想要让你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是觉得你诚意有些不足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原因是你们的疏忽不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:30.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,诚意…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我现在还没地方可去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:37.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,能让我住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要被改造得很宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:44.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还要有许多他种族女孩子一起寄宿的家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能对阿剌克涅族有厌恶感的宿主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不然  生活也会不方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:55.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:59.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样的条件确实相当有限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只有一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:03.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,能符合你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:15.13,标题,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H45414C&}「MON和阿剌克涅的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}全员立刻离开这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:26.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}Darling君可能遭到感染了  要进行隔离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}如果病毒突然突变  出现能感染他种族的强力新型病毒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:35.00,标题,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&\pos(646,461)}「身体不适的日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:34.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}那就要变成关乎他种族存亡的爆发性感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.30,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其一  不要在意他人的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.86,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,要大胆以及慎重地选择目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:23.40,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其二  日常问候要适度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:26.88,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,当做好心理准备的话  就上阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:30.64,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其三  发现机会就要迅速瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:32.27,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,开火开火开火开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:34.76,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其四  不需要去顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:37.64,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最后确实给目标的心致命一击而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:42.35,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要有爱的话  就算只有一分也足够
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:48.57,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,比那个更重要的是  遵循欲望的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:51.58,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,冲吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.19,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘿！亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:57.00,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为有你在所以才会是最强的是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:59.63,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果能一直在一起那就是最棒的不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.16,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,无论前方会遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.96,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要和你就 All OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:07.53,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如今以无庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:10.27,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,这肯定就是宇宙第一的爱对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:14.65,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,等不及你的答案  我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:19.52,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最高速坠入爱河！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.30,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,一つ、人目ばっかり気にしてないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.86,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,大胆に、かつ慎重にターゲットを決める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:23.40,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,二つ、あいさつはほどほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:26.88,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,ココロの準備が済んだら、いざ尋常に！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:30.64,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,三つ、見つけた隙は即座に狙い定め
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:32.27,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,撃つべし撃つべし撃つべし撃つべし！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:34.76,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,四つ、遠慮は必要ないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:37.64,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,あとは確実にハートを仕留めるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:42.35,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,愛だったら、ほんのちょっとでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:48.57,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,それより何より、欲望のおもむくまま、
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:51.58,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,さぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.19,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,ねぇだぁりん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:57.00,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,キミがいるから最強じゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:59.63,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,ずっと一緒なら最高じゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.16,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,この先何があったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.96,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,キミとなら All OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:07.53,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,もはやこれは紛れもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:10.27,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,宇宙で一番のLOVEなんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:14.65,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,答え待ちきれないんだよ、もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:19.52,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,最高速 Fall in Love！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:39.31,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,OY! OY! OY! Hey Sumisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:43.35,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,OY! OY! OY! Hey Sumisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.52,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,点燃手中拥有的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.41,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,毫无疑问的个人主义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.94,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,还记得吗随时光流逝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.97,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,真实如同海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.80,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,这不是逃跑是脚停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:56.64,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,那才是我的美学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:59.29,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,规律对我自身来说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:00.97,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:05.43,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,徒劳无功(徒劳无功) 功过事迹(功过事迹)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:09.62,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,扭扭腰(扭扭腰) 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.51,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我们代表正义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.35,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我们不容置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:18.02,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果真实是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.63,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！场面大话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:23.28,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:27.09,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是稍微说一点而已...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:35.79,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,愿我的心能获得安宁...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:50.21,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,710)}(OY！OY！OY！Hey Sumisu！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:39.31,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,(オイ！オイ！オイ！Hey スミス！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:43.35,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,(オイ！オイ！オイ！Hey スミス！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.52,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,その手に持った権力を発火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.33,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,紛れもないエゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.93,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,覚えてますか過去に流した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.97,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,真実は蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.80,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,逃げるわけじゃなくだいたい足掻く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:56.53,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,それが美学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:59.29,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,規律がどうの自分の中では
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:00.83,ED-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,意味が無い
